---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
import ImprintAddressComponent from '../../components/ImprintAddress.astro';

const usageSnippet = `---
import { ImprintAddress } from 'comet-astro';
---

<ImprintAddress
  name="Comet Studio GmbH"
  street="Rosenthaler Straße 40"
  postalCode="10178"
  city="Berlin"
  country="Germany"
  email="hello@comet.studio"
  phone="+49 30 123456"
  website="https://comet.studio"
  vatId="DE123456789"
  register="Amtsgericht Berlin, HRB 123456"
  size="md"
  layout="default"
/>`;
---

<DocsLayout
  title="ImprintAddress"
  description="Accessible legal address block with AAA contrast, semantic markup, and structured data support."
>
  <section class="space-y-4">
    <p class="text-base text-slate-100">
      ImprintAddress provides a WCAG AAA compliant component for displaying
      legal imprint and contact information. Built with semantic HTML and
      structured data markup for optimal accessibility and SEO.
    </p>
    <p class="text-base text-slate-200">
      The component supports flexible layouts, responsive sizing, and proper
      microdata markup following Schema.org Organization and PostalAddress
      standards for enhanced search engine understanding.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-10 space-y-6">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Props</h2>
    <dl class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <div
        class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-700/75 bg-slate-900/60 p-4 shadow-sm"
      >
        <dt
          class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-200"
        >
          name
        </dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">
          Organization or business name. Required field displayed as the main
          heading with semantic markup.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div
        class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-700/75 bg-slate-900/60 p-4 shadow-sm"
      >
        <dt
          class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-200"
        >
          size?
        </dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">
          Controls typography scale. Options: <code>"sm"</code>, <code
            >"md"</code
          >,
          <code>"lg"</code>. Defaults to <code>"md"</code> with responsive sizing.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div
        class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-700/75 bg-slate-900/60 p-4 shadow-sm"
      >
        <dt
          class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-200"
        >
          layout?
        </dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">
          Spacing configuration: <code>"compact"</code>, <code>"default"</code>,
          <code>"expanded"</code>. Affects vertical spacing between sections.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div
        class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-700/75 bg-slate-900/60 p-4 shadow-sm"
      >
        <dt
          class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-200"
        >
          showLabels?
        </dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">
          Display section labels for "Address", "Contact", and "Legal
          Information". Defaults to <code>false</code> for cleaner appearance.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div
        class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-700/75 bg-slate-900/60 p-4 shadow-sm sm:col-span-2"
      >
        <dt
          class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-200"
        >
          Address Fields
        </dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">
          <code>street?</code>, <code>postalCode?</code>, <code>city?</code>,
          <code>country?</code> - All optional address components with proper microdata
          markup and responsive formatting.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div
        class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-700/75 bg-slate-900/60 p-4 shadow-sm sm:col-span-2"
      >
        <dt
          class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-200"
        >
          Contact Fields
        </dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">
          <code>email?</code>, <code>phone?</code>, <code>website?</code> - Contact
          links with accessible labels, proper protocols, and WCAG AAA compliant
          focus states.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div
        class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-700/75 bg-slate-900/60 p-4 shadow-sm sm:col-span-2"
      >
        <dt
          class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-200"
        >
          Legal Fields
        </dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">
          <code>vatId?</code>, <code>register?</code> - Legal identifiers for VAT
          number and business registration details.
        </dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-10 space-y-6">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Usage</h2>
    <p class="text-base text-slate-200">
      Import the component and provide the required name field along with any
      optional contact and address information. The component automatically
      handles semantic markup and accessibility features.
    </p>
    <pre
      class="overflow-x-auto rounded-lg border border-slate-700/70 bg-slate-950/80 p-4 text-sm text-slate-50 shadow-inner">
      <code class="language-astro">{usageSnippet}</code>
    </pre>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-10 space-y-8">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Basic Example</h2>
    <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/30 p-6">
      <ImprintAddressComponent
        name="Comet Studio GmbH"
        street="Rosenthaler Straße 40"
        postalCode="10178"
        city="Berlin"
        country="Germany"
        email="hello@comet.studio"
        phone="+49 30 123456"
        website="https://comet.studio"
        vatId="DE123456789"
        register="Amtsgericht Berlin Charlottenburg, HRB 123456"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-10 space-y-8">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Sizes</h2>
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-100 mb-3">Small</h3>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/30 p-4">
          <ImprintAddressComponent
            name="Small Business Ltd."
            street="Main Street 123"
            postalCode="12345"
            city="Sample City"
            email="info@small-business.com"
            size="sm"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-100 mb-3">
          Medium (Default)
        </h3>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/30 p-4">
          <ImprintAddressComponent
            name="Medium Corp"
            street="Business Avenue 456"
            postalCode="67890"
            city="Corporate City"
            email="contact@medium-corp.com"
            phone="+1 555 123 4567"
            size="md"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-100 mb-3">Large</h3>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/30 p-4">
          <ImprintAddressComponent
            name="Large Enterprise Inc."
            street="Enterprise Blvd 789"
            postalCode="13579"
            city="Metro City"
            country="United States"
            email="info@large-enterprise.com"
            phone="+1 555 987 6543"
            website="https://large-enterprise.com"
            size="lg"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-10 space-y-8">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Layouts</h2>
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-100 mb-3">Compact Layout</h3>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/30 p-4">
          <ImprintAddressComponent
            name="Compact Design Co."
            street="Design Street 100"
            postalCode="24680"
            city="Creative City"
            email="hello@compact-design.com"
            layout="compact"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-100 mb-3">Default Layout</h3>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/30 p-4">
          <ImprintAddressComponent
            name="Standard Solutions LLC"
            street="Solution Avenue 200"
            postalCode="97531"
            city="Standard City"
            email="info@standard-solutions.com"
            phone="+1 555 246 8024"
            layout="default"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-100 mb-3">Expanded Layout</h3>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/30 p-4">
          <ImprintAddressComponent
            name="Spacious Studios"
            street="Studio Lane 300"
            postalCode="86420"
            city="Artistic City"
            email="contact@spacious-studios.com"
            phone="+1 555 135 7920"
            website="https://spacious-studios.com"
            layout="expanded"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-10 space-y-8">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">With Labels</h2>
    <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/30 p-6">
      <ImprintAddressComponent
        name="Labeled Business Corp"
        street="Professional Drive 400"
        postalCode="75319"
        city="Business District"
        country="United States"
        email="admin@labeled-business.com"
        phone="+1 555 159 2634"
        website="https://labeled-business.com"
        vatId="US987654321"
        register="State of Business, Corp. #123456"
        showLabels={true}
        layout="expanded"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-10 space-y-4">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Accessibility</h2>
    <p class="text-base text-slate-200">
      ImprintAddress follows WCAG AAA guidelines with contrast ratios exceeding
      7:1 for all text and interactive elements. The component uses semantic
      <code>&lt;address&gt;</code> markup with proper roles and labels.
    </p>
    <p class="text-base text-slate-200">
      Contact links include descriptive aria-labels and screen reader
      announcements for external links. Focus states use high-contrast ring
      indicators with proper offset for visibility against any background.
    </p>
    <p class="text-base text-slate-200">
      Structured data markup follows Schema.org standards for Organization and
      PostalAddress, enabling search engines and assistive technologies to
      understand and present the information appropriately.
    </p>
    <p class="text-base text-slate-200">
      The component supports keyboard navigation with logical tab order and
      responsive design that maintains usability across all device sizes and
      zoom levels up to 200%.
    </p>
  </section>
</DocsLayout>
